## Autonomous Workflow

Execute the canonical project workflow for feature or maintenance brief: **$ARGUMENTS**

## Workflow Stages

1. Run `/speckit.specify`
2. Run `/speckit.clarify` when critical ambiguity remains
3. Run `/speckit.plan`
4. If planning requires new technology outside the approved stack, STOP and request explicit approval
5. Run `/speckit.tasks`
6. Run `/speckit.analyze`
7. Run `/speckit.implement`
8. Run the blocking validation gates:
{{BLOCKING_GATES_INDENTED}}
9. Run the observational validation gates and record the outcome:
{{OBSERVATIONAL_GATES_INDENTED}}
10. Update `TEST_REPORT.md`
11. Update `REVIEW_REPORT.md`
12. Run a mandatory fix round
13. Re-run all validation gates
14. Generate `SNAPSHOT.md` last
